[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"OSS Capital's "},{"href":"https://twitter.com/JosephJacks_","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Joseph Jacks"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":", who led our seed round of funding, said something that has stuck with me ever since he said it:"}]},{"type":"block-quote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"You are building something that is generationally important"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"(No pressure ðŸ˜…)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"I believe it. But Remix can't become a generationally important technology without being community driven, and it can't be community driven if it's not developed in the open."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Today we are completely opening up our development process."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"No invisible roadmap"}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"No surprise features"}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"No wondering when a bug is going to be fixed"}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"No private issue tracker (goodbye Linear ðŸ˜¢ it's not you, it's me)."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading-two","children":[{"text":"Public Roadmap"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Our "},{"href":"https://github.com/orgs/remix-run/projects/5/views/1","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Roadmap"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":" is now public. It's a GitHub project that shows what we've got planned, in progress, pre-release, and recently shipped. You can easily see if your bug is getting fixed, your pet feature is coming soon, or know when you can try out pre-released features using our nightly builds."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":""}]},{"src":"https://media.graphassets.com/pobGHK5RQAWpttnSkuzY","type":"image","title":"roadmap.jpg","width":2000,"handle":"pobGHK5RQAWpttnSkuzY","height":1125,"children":[{"text":""}],"mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"heading-two","children":[{"text":"Open Development Process"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"To make our development "},{"text":"community driven","italic":true},{"text":", we'll be doing all of our planning in the open and encourage developers using Remix to participate. Here's how features get into the Roadmap."}]},{"type":"numbered-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Contributors"},{"text":" (that's anybody!) add a Proposal to "},{"href":"https://github.com/remix-run/remix/discussions/categories/proposals","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Remix Proposals"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":" or "},{"href":"https://github.com/remix-run/react-router/discussions/categories/proposals","type":"link","children":[{"text":"React Router Proposals"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":"."}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"The Remix "}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Admin Team"}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":" accepts Proposals in the Roadmap Planning meeting."}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Proposals are accepted when the Admins create an "},{"bold":true,"text":"Issue"},{"text":" from the Proposal and add the issue to the Roadmap."}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"The Admins assign an "}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Owner"}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":" to the issue."}]},{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Owners may be contributors from inside or outside of the Remix team"}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Owners are responsible for shipping the feature including all decisions for APIs, behavior, and implementation."}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Owners organize the work with other contributors for larger issues."}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Owners create an "},{"bold":true,"text":"RFC"},{"text":" from the Proposal and then development can begin."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"In other words: Proposal â†’ Roadmap â†’ RFC â†’ Develop â†’ Ship"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"For more details on how to participate, see the "},{"href":"https://github.com/remix-run/remix/blob/main/docs/pages/contributing.md","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Contributing Page"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":"."}]},{"type":"heading-two","children":[{"text":"Roadmap Planning Live Stream"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Not only is the development opening up, but we'll be live streaming our Roadmap Planning meeting too:"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Watch the stream on our "},{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/c/Remix-Run/streams","type":"link","children":[{"text":"YouTube Channel"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":""}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Remix Admins will review Proposals and verified bugs and add them to the Roadmap."}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Other members of the Remix team and outside collaborators will often attend."}]}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"type":"list-item-child","children":[{"text":"Everybody is invited to participate in our "},{"href":"https://rmx.as/discord","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Discord"}],"openInNewTab":false},{"text":" channel #roadmap-livestream-chat"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"That's it! We'll see you on GitHub ðŸ¤—"}]}]